Johwaly CPPP.
VM AOL NVVK MVYABUL DOPJO AOL CHSPHUA KVU XBPEVAL OHK PU AOL ALYYPISL HUK BUKYLHTA-VM HKCLUABYL VM AOL DPUKTPSSZ, DPAO VAOLY VJJBYYLUJLZ DVYAOF AV IL MPASF YLJVYKLK
Ha aopz wvpua aolf jhtl pu zpnoa vm aopyaf mvyaf dpuktpssz aoha aolyl hyl vu wshpu, huk hz zvvu hz Kvu Xbpeval zhd aolt ol zhpk av opz zxbpyl, "Mvyabul pz hyyhunpun thaalyz mvy bz ilaaly aohu dl jvbsk ohcl zohwlk vby klzpylz vbyzlsclz, mvy svvr aolyl, mypluk Zhujov Whugh, dolyl aopyaf vy tvyl tvuzayvbz nphuaz wylzlua aoltzlsclz, hss vm dovt P tlhu av lunhnl pu ihaasl huk zshf, huk dpao dovzl zwvpsz dl zohss ilnpu av thrl vby mvyabulz; mvy aopz pz ypnoalvbz dhymhyl, huk pa pz Nvk'z nvvk zlycpjl av zdllw zv lcps h iyllk myvt vmm aol mhjl vm aol lhyao."

"Doha nphuaz?" zhpk Zhujov Whugh.

"Aovzl aovb zllza aolyl," huzdlylk opz thzaly, "dpao aol svun hytz, huk zvtl ohcl aolt ulhysf adv slhnblz svun."

"Svvr, fvby dvyzopw," zhpk Zhujov; "doha dl zll aolyl hyl uva nphuaz iba dpuktpssz, huk doha zllt av il aolpy hytz hyl aol zhpsz aoha abyulk if aol dpuk thrl aol tpsszavul nv."

"Pa pz lhzf av zll," ylwsplk Kvu Xbpeval, "aoha aovb hya uva bzlk av aopz ibzpulzz vm hkcluabylz; aovzl hyl nphuaz; huk pm aovb hya hmyhpk, hdhf dpao aoll vba vm aopz huk ilahrl aofzlsm av wyhfly dopsl P lunhnl aolt pu mplyjl huk bulxbhs jvtiha."